00:03:15,720 --> 00:03:18,860
Hoping to catch me off guard?

17
00:03:21,940 --> 00:03:24,660
I've got a surprise for you too.

18
00:03:24,660 --> 00:03:27,460
I fed your girl

19
00:03:31,200 --> 00:03:34,160
a micro-bomb.

20
00:03:34,810 --> 00:03:38,700
Luo, you're dying.

21
00:03:38,700 --> 00:03:43,980
And I've arranged a splendid
fireworks show for you.

22
00:03:46,300 --> 00:03:48,360
Looking forward to it?

23
00:04:13,280 --> 00:04:15,200
This is the place.

24
00:04:15,200 --> 00:04:16,700
Let's go.

25
00:05:10,080 --> 00:05:11,820
Aoki. Aoki!

26
00:05:11,820 --> 00:05:13,420
Wake up, Aoki.

27
00:05:13,420 --> 00:05:15,020
Aoki!

28
00:05:16,640 --> 00:05:19,120
Aoki!

29
00:05:21,620 --> 00:05:23,620
Aoki, they're fighting inside.

30
00:05:23,620 --> 00:05:24,940
What do we do?

31
00:05:24,940 --> 00:05:27,180
They're fighting.

32
00:05:27,180 --> 00:05:28,820
Fighting?

33
00:05:31,420 --> 00:05:33,200
Where?

34
00:05:56,760 --> 00:05:58,520
Luo Ren.

35
