I'm sorry.

37
00:06:11,640 --> 00:06:13,300
Sorry.

38
00:06:13,300 --> 00:06:15,200
Sorry.

39
00:07:38,020 --> 00:07:39,600
Go.

40
00:07:42,700 --> 00:07:44,600
Now.

41
00:07:45,580 --> 00:07:48,440
Hong Sha, keep pressure on his wound.

42
00:08:33,160 --> 00:08:34,960
Dare attack my sect?

43
00:08:34,960 --> 00:08:36,360
I'll kill you!

44
00:08:36,360 --> 00:08:38,060
Cao!

45
00:08:41,240 --> 00:08:42,880
Get back here!

46
00:08:55,140 --> 00:08:59,040
Sorry, I missed.

47
00:08:59,040 --> 00:09:02,680
Found anything when you searched Leopard?

48
00:09:02,680 --> 00:09:04,220
Whatever.

49
00:09:04,220 --> 00:09:07,400
Thought I was done for, so I took everything.

50
00:09:09,020 --> 00:09:10,840
Get Thirteen-Thousand to bring the car.

51
00:09:10,840 --> 00:09:12,260
Luo Ren's fading fast.

52
00:09:12,260 --> 00:09:14,080
Hurry!

53
00:09:17,940 --> 00:09:20,140
Hear that? Gunfight inside.

54
00:09:20,140 --> 00:09:22,740
- Where?
- Right in there.

55
00:09:34,740 --> 00:09:36,420
Leopard?

56
00:09:38,940 --> 00:09:40,500
Can we catch up?

57
00:09:45,320 --> 00:09:47,440
Wrong turn, Aoki.

58
00:09:56,500 --> 00:09:58,680
- Aoki!
- Hold on tight.

59
00:10:21,500 --> 00:10:23,060
Thirteen-Thousand?

60
00:10:24,980 --> 00:10:27,380
Where's the car?

61
00:10:28,500 --> 00:10:30,980
Where did that guy go?

62
00:10:36,220 --> 00:10:38,640
Is she dead?

63
00:11:36,620 --> 00:11:38,380
Leopard!

64
00:11:56,460 --> 00:11:58,300
Come on!

65
00:12:27,420 --> 00:12:29,100
Free.

66
00:12:44,540 --> 00:12:46,780
We all made it back safely.

67
00:12:48,180 --> 00:12:49,820
Not good.

68
00:12:50,780 --> 00:12:54,040
The doctor said the chances of him waking up...

69
00:12:54,660 --> 00:12:57,700
Senior Master's still at Heisha,
handling the aftermath.

70
00:12:57,700 --> 00:13:00,000
We'll return as soon as we can.

71
00:13:02,420 --> 00:13:04,620
Where's Ren?

72
00:13:05,440 --> 00:13:07,540
Where's Ren?

73
00:13:07,540 --> 00:13:09,220
How is he?

74
00:13:09,220 --> 00:13:11,000
He's sleeping.

75
00:13:19,040 --> 00:13:20,660
Alright.

76
00:13:20,660 --> 00:13:22,520
Be careful.

77
00:13:28,540 --> 00:13:30,620
People...

78
00:13:30,620 --> 00:13:35,640
Sometimes people really are just monsters.

79
00:13:38,440 --> 00:13:40,740
Mr. Kun, any luck with the Feng-Huang-Luan Buckle?

80
00:13:40,740 --> 00:13:42,100
 

81
00:13:42,100 --> 00:13:43,400
Not great.

82
00:13:43,400 --> 00:13:47,060
I've asked those who have any leads to send me photos and videos first.

83
00:13:47,060 --> 00:13:49,740
Gone through dozens with phoenix motifs.

84
00:13:49,740 --> 00:13:50,900
None of them is the right one.

85
00:13:50,900 --> 00:13:53,380
But we're on the right track.

86
00:13:55,980 --> 00:13:59,020
Radishie still hasn't woken up?

87
00:13:59,640 --> 00:14:01,260
No.

88
00:14:03,740 --> 00:14:07,140
Why have all of you collapsed like this?

89
00:14:07,140 --> 00:14:09,640
I need to figure something out.

90
00:14:16,540 --> 00:14:18,600
Here to see your boyfriend again?

91
00:14:19,340 --> 00:14:22,380
Heard her boyfriend might never wake up.

92
00:14:24,160 --> 00:14:25,860
 

93
00:14:25,860 --> 00:14:28,020
Hong Sha, where should I put this balloon?

94
00:14:28,020 --> 00:14:30,000
Not there. Lower.

95
00:14:30,000 --> 00:14:31,420
It's supposed to be a heart shape.

96
00:14:31,420 --> 00:14:33,420
Too much in the middle, right?

97
00:14:33,420 --> 00:14:34,700
Higher on this side.

98
00:14:34,700 --> 00:14:37,260
- Lift the left side a bit, right?
- Let me see.

99
00:14:37,260 --> 00:14:39,380
 
What are you...?

100
00:14:39,380 --> 00:14:41,520
Mu Dai, you're here.

101
00:14:41,520 --> 00:14:43,020
Come here.

102
00:14:43,020 --> 00:14:45,200
- What is this?
- I want to show you something.

103
00:14:46,020 --> 00:14:48,180
Luo, wake up soon.

104
00:14:48,180 --> 00:14:49,620
Mu Dai misses you.

105
00:14:49,620 --> 00:14:52,220
We all miss you.

106
