107
00:15:07,580 --> 00:15:09,340
Welcome to Phoenix Pavilion.

108
00:15:09,340 --> 00:15:11,220
Come back again.
Bring friends, and I'll give you a discount.

109
00:15:11,220 --> 00:15:13,300
- Then I'll have the udon.
- Got it.

110
00:15:13,300 --> 00:15:15,060
Extra cilantro on mine.

111
00:15:15,060 --> 00:15:16,380
- Understood.
- Thank you for coming.

112
00:15:16,380 --> 00:15:17,480
Welcome to Phoenix Pavilion.

113
00:15:17,480 --> 00:15:18,900
Extra cilantro on your noodles, right?

114
00:15:18,900 --> 00:15:24,335
 ♫ In the deepest night, longing takes shape ♫ 

115
00:15:24,335 --> 00:15:31,200
 ♫ Warm memories slowly embrace you tight ♫ 

116
00:15:31,200 --> 00:15:36,460
 ♫ The path of growth is inevitably lonely ♫ 

117
00:15:36,460 --> 00:15:38,020
Mu Dai.

118
00:15:38,940 --> 00:15:44,620
If Luo Ren never wakes up, will you keep waiting for him?

119
00:15:44,620 --> 00:15:46,060
Yes.

120
00:15:46,720 --> 00:15:49,100
Of course, I'll wait.

121
00:15:49,100 --> 00:15:52,860
I'm waiting for someone worth waiting for.

122
00:15:52,860 --> 00:15:56,060
Every day, I hope with all my heart
that he wakes up.

123
00:15:56,060 --> 00:15:58,635
 ♫ Stubbornness and courage keep you strong ♫ 

124
00:15:58,635 --> 00:16:01,940
 ♫ In the gaps of time within memories ♫ 

125
00:16:01,940 --> 00:16:04,160
Luo Ren, you know what?

126
00:16:04,160 --> 00:16:05,640
 Leopard is paralyzed. 

127
00:16:05,640 --> 00:16:07,720
 She's lost all normal mobility. 

128
00:16:07,720 --> 00:16:09,320
 She was handed over
to the stabilization organization, 

129
00:16:09,320 --> 00:16:11,720
 and she will face sentencing and imprisonment. 

130
00:16:11,720 --> 00:16:14,400
 Tasha went back to Western Australia. 

131
00:16:14,400 --> 00:16:19,220
 My senior contacted her guardian and got her into the best rehab center. 

132
00:16:19,220 --> 00:16:21,160
 They ran a mental assessment, 

133
00:16:21,160 --> 00:16:24,380
 but the results weren't good. 

134
00:16:24,380 --> 00:16:27,180
 She won't return to a normal life anytime soon. 

135
00:16:27,180 --> 00:16:32,405
 ♫ Companionship and care
are like gentle beams of light ♫ 

136
00:16:32,405 --> 00:16:38,120
 ♫ Embark on the journey, healing all loneliness ♫ 

137
00:16:38,120 --> 00:16:41,020
 ♫ Waiting together for the sunrise ♫ 

138
00:16:41,020 --> 00:16:42,500
Kneel.

139
00:16:47,700 --> 00:16:49,260
Bow.

140
00:16:54,260 --> 00:16:57,980
 

141
00:16:57,980 --> 00:17:02,220
Don't forget to buy cabbage,
pork ribs, and potatoes.

142
00:17:02,220 --> 00:17:04,700
And get a few bottles
of good Huangjiu if they have it.

143
00:17:04,700 --> 00:17:06,140
Got it.

144
00:17:06,140 --> 00:17:09,700
Hong Sha's the reliable one around here.

145
00:17:09,700 --> 00:17:11,340
Tell me about it.

146
00:17:11,340 --> 00:17:12,620
I don't work for free though.

147
00:17:12,620 --> 00:17:14,660
You should pay me on time.

148
00:17:14,660 --> 00:17:16,620
I've got debts to settle.

149
00:17:16,620 --> 00:17:18,680
Don't worry about it.

150
00:17:22,720 --> 00:17:24,480
Ren.

151
00:17:25,340 --> 00:17:27,220
Ren?

152
00:17:27,220 --> 00:17:29,260
You've been asleep for a month.

153
00:17:29,260 --> 00:17:31,540
When do you plan to wake up?

154
00:17:31,540 --> 00:17:34,880
What if I get used to only visiting you once

155
00:17:34,880 --> 00:17:39,380
every couple of weeks?

156
00:17:40,780 --> 00:17:42,820
The cycle of seven sevens is approaching.

157
00:17:42,820 --> 00:17:44,500
You can't keep sleeping.

158
00:17:44,500 --> 00:17:48,880
We're still waiting for you to lead us to subdue the seventh relic of ill omen.

159
00:17:59,460 --> 00:18:01,540
For that table over there.

160
00:18:06,240 --> 00:18:07,920
Aoki.

161
00:18:08,760 --> 00:18:10,540
What's wrong with Luo?

162
00:18:11,660 --> 00:18:14,480
I can't hear you.What's wrong with Luo?

163
00:18:30,580 --> 00:18:31,780
Luo Ren.

164
00:18:31,780 --> 00:18:34,380
Don't worry. He woke up once before.

165
00:18:34,380 --> 00:18:35,800
He asked me if you were safe.

166
00:18:35,800 --> 00:18:38,300
I told him everyone was safe.

167
00:18:38,300 --> 00:18:41,800
The doctor said it's a good sign.

168
00:18:42,540 --> 00:18:44,540
Family members don't need to worry.

169
00:18:47,620 --> 00:18:51,260
Since Luo Ren's out of danger,
I've booked a flight

170
00:18:52,311 --> 00:18:53,860
and will go home tomorrow.

171
00:18:53,860 --> 00:18:55,680
You're going back?

172
00:18:56,660 --> 00:18:59,540
Hey, Noriko.

173
00:19:00,660 --> 00:19:02,560
How are you doing?

174
00:19:07,340 --> 00:19:10,000
Wish you and Luo Ren happiness together.

175
00:19:10,900 --> 00:19:13,060
I'm entrusting him to you.

176
00:19:30,930 --> 00:19:37,800
 ♫ Whenever memories whisper silently ♫ 

177
00:19:37,800 --> 00:19:41,900
 ♫ Gazing at each other's burning teardrops ♫ 

178
00:19:44,600 --> 00:19:51,600
 ♫ Together we brave the storms of adversity, oh ♫ 

179
00:19:51,600 --> 00:19:55,320
 ♫ Only through reconciliation
can we find answers within ourselves ♫ 

180
00:19:55,320 --> 00:19:56,700
Ren.

181
00:19:56,700 --> 00:20:00,525
 ♫ This fickle fate ♫ 

182
00:20:00,525 --> 00:20:03,320
 ♫ Is like a cliff of thorns ♫ 

183
00:20:03,320 --> 00:20:06,482
 ♫ Through the pain we march on ♫ 

184
00:20:06,482 --> 00:20:07,520
You appear gaunt.

185
00:20:07,520 --> 00:20:09,445
 ♫ Dreams arrive where perseverance holds fast ♫ 

186
00:20:09,445 --> 00:20:10,540
So haggard.

187
00:20:10,540 --> 00:20:16,440
 ♫ See our future, I believe, I believe,
I believe love's horizon awaits ♫ 

188
00:20:16,440 --> 00:20:18,629
How long was I out?

189
00:20:18,629 --> 00:20:20,837
Over a month.

190
00:20:20,837 --> 00:20:22,382
Are you hungry?

191
00:20:22,382 --> 00:20:23,903
Want something to eat?

192
00:20:23,903 --> 00:20:29,440
 ♫ Through all the time we've spent together ♫ 

193
00:20:29,440 --> 00:20:30,520
Back then...

194
00:20:30,520 --> 00:20:34,440
 ♫ Countless memories forever ♫ 

195
00:20:34,440 --> 00:20:35,740
Did I hurt you?

196
00:20:35,740 --> 00:20:40,500
 ♫ Just want to slowly, slowly hold you tight ♫ 

197
00:20:40,500 --> 00:20:42,540
That was life-or-death combat.

198
00:20:42,540 --> 00:20:44,680
My injuries were nothing.

199
00:20:44,680 --> 00:20:46,908
They healed long ago.

200
00:20:46,908 --> 00:20:47,940
Don't worry.

201
00:20:47,940 --> 00:20:50,372
 ♫ I'll take your hand ♫ 

202
00:20:50,372 --> 00:20:56,743
 ♫ till the world ends ♫ 

203
00:20:58,065 --> 00:20:59,130
Did it hurt?

204
00:20:59,130 --> 00:21:05,120
 ♫ See our future, I believe, I believe, I believe love's horizon awaits ♫ 

205
00:21:05,120 --> 00:21:11,480
 ♫ Just want to slowly love you
with all my hope, oh ♫ 

206
00:21:11,480 --> 00:21:12,598
I'm sorry.

207
00:21:12,598 --> 00:21:14,640
 ♫ Through all the time we've spent together ♫ 

208
00:21:14,640 --> 00:21:16,680
This time,

209
00:21:17,773 --> 00:21:19,568
I didn't do well enough.

210
00:21:19,568 --> 00:21:22,550
Don't say that.

211
00:21:22,550 --> 00:21:24,740
You've done a great job.

212
00:21:24,740 --> 00:21:28,920
All along, you've been leading
and taking care of us.

213
00:21:28,920 --> 00:21:32,160
Now it's my turn, our turn to take care of you.

214
00:21:32,160 --> 00:21:34,340
And don't be sad.

215
00:21:34,340 --> 00:21:35,440
It's alright now.

216
00:21:35,440 --> 00:21:36,740
Everyone made it through.

217
00:21:36,740 --> 00:21:38,640
Everyone's safe.

218
00:21:38,640 --> 00:21:39,960
Isn't that good enough?

219
00:21:39,960 --> 00:21:42,160
 ♫ I'll take your hand till the world ends ♫ 

220
00:21:42,160 --> 00:21:44,160
Right?

221
00:21:44,160 --> 00:21:46,780
Is it tiring for you
to listen to me talk like this?

222
00:21:46,780 --> 00:21:50,500
We can always talk later if you need to rest.

223
00:21:50,500 --> 00:21:52,165
Not at all.

224
00:21:54,000 --> 00:21:56,100
Mu Dai.

225
00:21:56,100 --> 00:21:59,700
Back then, we were fighting
each other in that cage.

226
00:21:59,700 --> 00:22:01,640
 ♫ Through all the time we've spent together ♫ 

227
00:22:01,640 --> 00:22:03,680
How did you manage to snap out of it?

228
00:22:05,675 --> 00:22:07,920
 ♫ Countless memories forever ♫ 

229
00:22:07,920 --> 00:22:11,880
I summoned Dark Mu Dai.

230
00:22:11,880 --> 00:22:14,960
From where I was trapped,
I could see the signal tower.

231
00:22:14,960 --> 00:22:18,260
I timed it. The signal came every three seconds.

232
00:22:18,260 --> 00:22:20,900
Perfect for hypnosis.

233
00:22:34,920 --> 00:22:36,500
Leopard wants to brainwash us

234
00:22:36,500 --> 00:22:39,720
and turn us into another
Tasha to use against Luo Ren.

235
00:22:39,720 --> 00:22:42,220
We can't let her succeed.

236
00:22:42,220 --> 00:22:43,965
Of course not.

237
00:22:43,965 --> 00:22:47,545
Luckily, she never knew I existed.

238
00:22:49,740 --> 00:22:52,500
You're exhausted. Sit down.

239
00:22:53,880 --> 00:22:55,220
Here.

240
00:22:57,400 --> 00:23:00,240
Leopard wasn't easy to fool.

241
00:23:00,240 --> 00:23:02,820
Pretending to be brainwashed is impossible.

242
00:23:04,720 --> 00:23:11,300
So one of us has to sleep while the other surrendered to it.

243
00:23:13,720 --> 00:23:18,300
I just couldn't figure out the trigger to break the hypnosis.

244
00:23:20,720 --> 00:23:22,920
Luo Ren's whistle.

245
00:23:22,920 --> 00:23:27,120
He said it was his signature trick.

246
00:23:27,120 --> 00:23:30,274
After hearing the whistle,
the sleeper will wake up,

247
00:23:30,274 --> 00:23:33,974
and the brainwashed one can't be kept.

248
00:23:33,974 --> 00:23:37,282
They must take their own life to eliminate future troubles.

249
00:23:39,340 --> 00:23:43,363
Why do you know everything?

250
00:23:43,363 --> 00:23:45,543
Because I am you.

251
00:23:49,900 --> 00:23:52,316
Brainwashing hurts.

252
00:23:52,316 --> 00:23:53,856
Let me take it.

253
00:24:00,096 --> 00:24:01,476
Don't cry.

254
00:24:01,476 --> 00:24:05,556
You little crybaby, this world is full of storms.

255
00:24:05,556 --> 00:24:08,196
I was made to protect us.

256
00:24:08,196 --> 00:24:10,676
Listen up, I'll fight this last battle

257
00:24:10,676 --> 00:24:13,576
as bravely as our master did.

258
00:24:15,916 --> 00:24:17,736
It's just a pity

259
00:24:20,116 --> 00:24:22,576
I won't get to see you take the field again.

260
00:24:28,356 --> 00:24:30,196
Don't be afraid.

261
00:24:31,156 --> 00:24:32,916
You're unbreakable.

262
00:24:32,916 --> 00:24:35,036
You'll come back alive.

263
00:24:39,021 --> 00:24:40,781
Ren.

264
00:24:45,916 --> 00:24:48,381
I...

265
00:24:48,381 --> 00:24:51,221
I miss her so much.

266
00:24:51,221 --> 00:24:53,096
Sometimes when I wake up
in the middle of the night,

267
00:24:53,096 --> 00:24:55,376
I feel so lonely.

268
00:24:55,956 --> 00:25:00,672
Like a part of me

269
00:25:00,672 --> 00:25:04,336
has been torn away.

270
00:25:10,376 --> 00:25:12,456
Yes, Mu Dai.

271
00:25:12,456 --> 00:25:17,696
People say growing up means the old self keeps tearing apart

272
00:25:17,696 --> 00:25:20,441
while the new self is being reforged.

273
00:25:20,441 --> 00:25:22,961
But I don't see it that way.

274
00:25:22,961 --> 00:25:27,636
I believe growing up is the old self constantly embracing the new self.

275
00:25:27,636 --> 00:25:30,076
